name: OWO-1 With Backup
Lore: 'Trade Federation battle droid leader assigned to take a squad and destroy what was left of the Jedi ambassadors. His mission went unaccomplished.',
Text: 'Requires +2 Force to use Landspeed. Power +1 for each opponent''s Jedi present. While with a battledroid at a site, draws two battle destiny if unable to otherwise. Opponent''s Force drains are -1 at adjacent sites.',
